OL,3,CKnifeman shot by police was 'lawfully
OL,4,Ckilled', jury finds
OL,6,FBodycam footage of Marius Ciolac
OL,7,Fsmashing a window and attacking police
OL,8,Fcars at Ascot Drive police station in
OL,9,FDerby
OL,11,FThe jury at an inquest into the
OL,12,Fshooting of a knifeman by Derbyshire
OL,13,FPolice in 2022 has concluded he was
OL,14,F"lawfully killed".
OL,16,FMarius Ciolac was shot by police after
OL,17,Fhe walked into the car park of Ascot
OL,18,FDrive police station in Derby on 7
OL,19,FOctober 2022, brandishing a 20cm-long
OL,20,Fknife and carrying a cat in a bag.
