OL,3,CKnifeman shot by police was 'lawfully
OL,4,Ckilled', jury finds
OL,6,FCCTV footage in court showed the 35-
OL,7,Fyear-old, who worked as a builder,
OL,8,Fattempting to smash his way into the
OL,9,Fstation and attacked police cars with
OL,10,Fhis knife.
OL,12,FThe four-week inquiry heard tasers, a
OL,13,Fbaton round and stun grenades were
OL,14,Fused on Mr Ciolac before he was shot
OL,15,Fin the abdomen.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/14
