OL,3,CKnifeman shot by police was 'lawfully
OL,4,Ckilled', jury finds
OL,6,FMr Ciolac, originally from Romania,
OL,7,Fwas given medical aid by paramedics at
OL,8,Fthe scene but went into cardiac
OL,9,Farrest. He was taken to Queen's
OL,10,FMedical Centre in Nottingham, where he
OL,11,Fdied at 11.25 am.
OL,13,FThe officer who shot Mr Ciolac,
OL,14,Freferred to in court as Officer A,
OL,15,Ftold Derby Coroner's Court he fired
OL,16,Fthe gun between 18 and 22 seconds
OL,17,Fafter he entered the car park with
OL,18,Fanother armed officer, called Officer
OL,19,FB.
