OL,6,FThe identity of both officers is
OL,7,Fprotected by an anonymity order.
OL,9,FThe officer said he told Mr Ciolac to
OL,10,Fdrop the knife, but did not say he was
OL,11,Farmed police, before he ran at him
OL,12,Fwith the weapon raised.
OL,14,FOfficer A told the jury: "He was
OL,15,Fclosing me down ` I was backpedalling.
OL,16,FI knew that negotiation, which would
OL,17,Fhave been my priority, was not working.
OL,19,F"We failed with the other less lethal
OL,20,Foptions. I felt I was left with no
OL,21,Fchoice.
