OL,6,F"It was the most dynamic and quick
OL,7,Fpolice incident I have been involved
OL,8,Fin. I have not been involved in
OL,9,Fanything that has happened as fast as
OL,10,Fthat.'
OL,12,FOfficer A said "He started walking
OL,13,Ftowards me. I raised my weapon and
OL,14,Faimed at him at that point and shouted
OL,15,Fanother command for him to drop the
OL,16,Fknife.
OL,18,F"He walked through the smoke of the
OL,19,Fstun grenade, there was no stopping
OL,20,Fwhen that stun grenade went off.
