OL,6,F"The fact he's walking towards me and
OL,7,Fclosing that gap means the risk could
OL,8,Fbe high".
OL,10,FOfficer A recalled Officer B having a
OL,11,Fbaton gun, which he heard go off but
OL,12,F"did not achieve its aim".
OL,14,FMr Ciolac's brother and sister
OL,15,Fattended part of the hearing remotely
OL,16,Fwith a Romanian interpreter.
OL,18,FThey asked Officer A about why he did
OL,19,Fnot shout "armed police" before he
OL,20,Ffired the gun.
