OL,6,FHis relatives said: "We have no
OL,7,Fexperience with the police. We find it
OL,8,Fhard to believe every member of the
OL,9,Fpublic in the country would know what
OL,10,Farmed police look like".
OL,12,FOfficer A replied: "We do routinely
OL,13,Fshout "armed police" when we arrive
OL,14,Fbut it is not a training standard. We
OL,15,Fdo what we think we need to do at the
OL,16,Ftime."
