OL,6,FA pathologist previously told the
OL,7,Finquest Mr Ciolac's cause of death was
OL,8,Fa gunshot wound to the abdomen and
OL,9,Fthere was "no evidence" to suggest he
OL,10,Fwas under the influence of drugs or
OL,11,Falcohol at the time of his death.
OL,13,FITV News Central's Correspondent Phil
OL,14,FBrewster asked Inspector Mason: "There
OL,15,Fmay be some people who watch this
OL,16,Ffootage and think police have shot
OL,17,Ffirst asked questions later."
OL,19,FHe responded saying: "I don't believe
OL,20,Fthat.
