OL,6,F"Officer A for example, if you
OL,7,Fconsider how close Mr Ciolac got to
OL,8,Fhim, with a potentially lethal weapon,
OL,9,Fthat officer took action in order to
OL,10,Fprotect himself.
OL,12,F"To ensure he was able to go home at
OL,13,Fnight and see him family."
OL,15,FMr Mason said: "Pulling the trigger on
