OL,6,FOur correspondent Phil Brewster asked
OL,7,FInspector Mason "Is there a scenario
OL,8,Fwhere perhaps, less volatile, less
OL,9,Fchaotic, less aggressive approach
OL,10,Fwould have paid more dividends rather
OL,11,Fthan all the noise we heard?"
OL,13,FHe responded saying "I don't believe
OL,14,Fso in this circumstance.
OL,16,F"If you look at the CCTV footage in
OL,17,Fdetail you've seen that Mr Ciolac has
OL,18,Ftried to force his way into a police
OL,19,Fstation use a great deal of force,
OL,20,Fsmashing windows.
