OL,6,F"There are unarmed officers in that
OL,7,Fbuilding.
OL,9,F"Mr Ciolac has taken the decision to
OL,10,Fclose those officers down.
OL,12,F"The officers went toward him
OL,13,Finitially but then withdrawn and then
OL,14,FMr Ciolac has run at those officers."
OL,16,FSergeant Anthony England was in the
OL,17,Fstation building with other officers
OL,18,Fwhen Mr Ciolac broke through the first
OL,19,Flayer of the double-glazed window.
